a product?

13:04.350 --> 13:06.653 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What differentiates it in the
market?

13:06.686 --> 13:08.321 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And, you know, it's funny.

13:08.354 --> 13:13.192 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
