composer.

51:20.110 --> 51:22.479 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that wasn't what he wanted
to be known
for.

51:22.513 --> 51:27.584 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, somehow, what snuck into
this piece was
the most exquisite, pure,
simple, beautiful

51:27.618 --> 51:30.254 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
melody that he ever wrote, "The
Swan."

51:30.287 --> 51:32.256 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Rob Kapilow,
thank you very
much.

